Sweetheart.

558
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:48,340
Why are you mad again?

559
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:52,100
I’m too tired

560
00:26:52,660 --> 00:26:53,700
to care for you.

561
00:26:57,380 --> 00:26:58,500
Fine.

562
00:27:01,580 --> 00:27:03,420
I’m going to take a bath first.

563
00:27:04,660 --> 00:27:05,620
I’ll be right back

564
00:27:05,620 --> 00:27:07,700
and help you relax yourself.

565
00:27:11,820 --> 00:27:12,340
By the way,

566
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:15,300
it’ll be our son's first birthday next week.

567
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:18,580
Commander Cao will also take office in the city.

568
00:27:19,500 --> 00:27:20,420
I’m wondering

569
00:27:20,740 --> 00:27:22,860
to do these two things together.

570
00:27:23,460 --> 00:27:24,580
It’s more convenient.

571
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:25,980
You may

572
00:27:26,700 --> 00:27:28,100
help me deal with it.

573
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:36,380
I am like a housekeeper.

574
00:27:37,380 --> 00:27:38,460
What did you say?

575
00:27:39,420 --> 00:27:40,500
Nothing.

576
00:27:40,700 --> 00:27:42,540
I will do it properly.

577
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:45,900
It's important.

578
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:48,100
Only you can make me feel at ease.

579
00:27:58,740 --> 00:28:02,500
(Cheng Mansion)

580
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:04,220
Put these stools in order.

581
00:28:06,380 --> 00:28:07,660
And also the tableware.

582
00:28:10,700 --> 00:28:11,740
This is the host table.

583
00:28:11,740 --> 00:28:13,380
Mr. Cheng will sit here with Commander.

584
00:28:13,620 --> 00:28:15,260
Move other tables away from it.

585
00:28:15,260 --> 00:28:16,580
Don’t disturb their talk.

586
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:18,980
Mrs. Cao.

587
00:28:19,420 --> 00:28:21,060
The things for Fortune Telling are all ready.

588
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:22,100
Take a look.

589
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:24,340
Mrs. Cao.

590
00:28:24,340 --> 00:28:25,060
Mr. Han.

591
00:28:27,180 --> 00:28:28,980
Don’t put the money far away.

592
00:28:29,340 --> 00:28:30,700
Baby can’t reach it.

593
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:35,500
Mr. Han.

594
00:28:35,620 --> 00:28:36,380
Mr. Cao.

595
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:37,620
The troupe is here.

596
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:38,620
How to arrange them?

597
00:28:39,300 --> 00:28:40,580
Take them to the rear rooms.

598
00:28:40,580 --> 00:28:42,140
You are supposed to know it.

599
00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:43,180
Bring them some food.

600
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:45,180
All the things are on me.

601
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:48,300
We haven’t held a party before.

602
00:28:48,300 --> 00:28:49,460
I know few about it.

603
00:28:49,460 --> 00:28:51,140
I’m going now. I’m going.

604
00:28:51,140 --> 00:28:51,780
Go.

605
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:52,260
Come back.

606
00:28:53,700 --> 00:28:54,780
Tell the maids in the mansion

607
00:28:54,780 --> 00:28:56,060
to stay away from the actors.

608
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:57,820
They may be badly influenced by them.

609
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:59,300
Yes. Yes.

610
00:28:59,460 --> 00:29:00,460
Where is Mrs. Cheng?

611
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:02,340
She...

612
00:29:02,780 --> 00:29:04,220
She is still sleeping.

613
00:29:06,660 --> 00:29:07,900
It shouldn't be.

614
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:10,020
She always gets up most early.

615
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:11,860
Today is a big day. How come she sleeps in?

616
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:21,580
Any change on my wife

617
00:29:22,460 --> 00:29:24,060
can’t escape my eyes.

618
00:29:24,620 --> 00:29:26,620
I see her hundreds of times a day.

619
00:29:27,740 --> 00:29:29,940
I keep her look in my mind each time.

620
00:29:52,460 --> 00:29:53,620
Mrs. Cheng.

621
00:29:54,140 --> 00:29:56,420
You’ve dressed up. Why don’t you go there?

622
00:29:56,740 --> 00:29:58,340
I’m busting around.

623
00:29:58,340 --> 00:29:58,820
Let’s go.

624
00:30:00,180 --> 00:30:01,220
Sis.

625
00:30:01,940 --> 00:30:03,300
What do you think

626
00:30:03,620 --> 00:30:04,900
of love?

627
00:30:09,620 --> 00:30:10,940
You don’t have a fever.

628
00:30:11,260 --> 00:30:13,060
What nonsense is that?

629
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:15,500
I watched many operas the other day.

630
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:21,460
If a woman never loves anyone,

631
00:30:21,460 --> 00:30:22,940
and is never loved by anyone,

632
00:30:23,940 --> 00:30:25,980
her life is pointless, isn’t it?

633
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:30,060
The operas are all fake stories

634
00:30:30,620 --> 00:30:32,580
to coax little girls.

635
00:30:33,300 --> 00:30:34,180
Fine.

636
00:30:34,180 --> 00:30:36,100
Today is your son's first birthday.

637
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:37,460
A big day for you.

638
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:38,660
Come with me.

639
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:40,540
All the stories in operas are true.

640
00:30:42,180 --> 00:30:44,340
My cousin does love his wife.

641
00:30:46,860 --> 00:30:48,740
Your brother doesn't love me.

642
00:30:50,780 --> 00:30:53,100
Why do you think so?

643
00:30:54,260 --> 00:30:55,260
Let me ask you.

644
00:30:56,180 --> 00:30:59,220
Does Fengtai offend you?

645
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:00,420
No.

646
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:04,620
I think

647
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:08,260
he is different from others.

648
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:12,380
That’s it.

649
00:31:13,100 --> 00:31:14,700
Men

650
00:31:15,020 --> 00:31:16,980
are different from each other.

651
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:22,060
Look.

652
00:31:22,700 --> 00:31:24,140
Some men

653
00:31:24,580 --> 00:31:26,580
tend to speak love out.

654
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:28,340
Some men

655
00:31:28,740 --> 00:31:31,140
tend to hide love in the heart.

656
00:31:31,860 --> 00:31:32,980
You know some men

657
00:31:33,260 --> 00:31:35,260
have affairs with many women,

658
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,420
while some men

659
00:31:36,420 --> 00:31:38,140
don’t understand love at all.

660
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:39,900
As for you,

661
00:31:40,140 --> 00:31:41,100
my brother is

662
00:31:41,100 --> 00:31:43,980
a clever man and you still complain about it.

663
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:45,340
I marry the Commander,

664
00:31:45,340 --> 00:31:46,860
a muscle-headed boor.

665
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:48,580
Should I kill myself?

666
00:31:49,740 --> 00:31:51,140
Really?

667
00:31:53,940 --> 00:31:54,780
Doesn’t he

668
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,140
understand love?

669
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:57,980
He doesn’t.

670
00:31:59,420 --> 00:32:00,140
Alright.

671
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,900
We may study operas later.

672
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:03,420
Hurry up and come with me.

673
00:32:03,420 --> 00:32:04,540
Commander is coming soon.

674
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:05,780
You’re the hostess.

675
00:32:05,780 --> 00:32:07,820
Don’t lose my face.

676
00:32:14,420 --> 00:32:16,340
Mr. Cheng. Congratulations.

677
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:18,940
Congratulations. Congratulations.

678
00:32:18,940 --> 00:32:20,500
Congratulations, Mr. Cheng.

679
00:32:20,940 --> 00:32:22,700
Help yourself, everyone.

680
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:23,700
Enjoy yourself.

681
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:26,460
Congratulations. Congratulations.

682
00:32:26,460 --> 00:32:28,300
-Let’s go and sit there.
-OK.

683
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,060
Mr. Cheng.

684
00:32:31,540 --> 00:32:33,660
Mr. Cheng, You may wait at the door.

685
00:32:33,660 --> 00:32:35,580
Cao is arriving as we speak.

686
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:36,780
Not so soon.

687
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:38,540
He is a commander.

688
00:32:38,780 --> 00:32:41,220
He’ll be late to show his identity.

689
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:43,660
Does Shuiyun Theater come here?

690
00:32:43,780 --> 00:32:45,340
Yes, from the northeastern gate.

691
00:32:45,340 --> 00:32:47,060
Mrs. Cao has arranged it.

692
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:50,260
I’m going to see them.

693
00:32:56,980 --> 00:32:58,660
Hey. How could it be?

694
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:00,060
It was sung by me.

695
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:00,900
How come?

696
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:01,780
Isn’t it obvious?

697
00:33:01,780 --> 00:33:03,460
Leader decided it long ago.

698
00:33:03,660 --> 00:33:04,620
Why didn’t you say it earlier?

699
00:33:04,620 --> 00:33:05,940
Do you think of it now?

700
00:33:06,020 --> 00:33:06,580
No way.

701
00:33:06,580 --> 00:33:07,300
Leader.

702
00:33:07,300 --> 00:33:08,380
I will sing this part.

703
00:33:08,380 --> 00:33:09,620
Don’t let her sing.

704
00:33:10,660 --> 00:33:11,380
Mr. Cheng.

705
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:12,500
Stop arguing.

706
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:14,060
-You may have a fight.
-Leader.

707
00:33:14,060 --> 00:33:15,020
I’m going to the toilet.

708
00:33:15,020 --> 00:33:15,940
Don’t go to the toilet.

709
00:33:16,140 --> 00:33:17,300
- Talk about it. - Leader. Don’t go.

710
00:33:17,500 --> 00:33:18,940
- You should decide it. - What to do? Tell me.

711
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:24,260
Greetings, Mr. Cheng.

712
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:27,100
I come to see

713
00:33:27,100 --> 00:33:28,540
if your performance is ready.

714
00:33:29,260 --> 00:33:30,260
It doesn’t seem

715
00:33:31,260 --> 00:33:32,700
a right time.

716
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:35,220
Sorry.

717
00:33:36,220 --> 00:33:36,940
Oh, right.

718
00:33:37,460 --> 00:33:38,460
Listen to me.

719
00:33:38,900 --> 00:33:40,740
When you perform on the stage,

720
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:43,660
I’ll let reporters take photos under the stage.

721
00:33:44,060 --> 00:33:45,980
When it’s reported tomorrow that

722
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:49,340
Mr. Shang’s excellent performance

723
00:33:49,580 --> 00:33:51,020
makes Commander Cao pleased,

724
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:53,980
your problem will be solved.

725
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:58,300
The debt I owe you is too much to repay.

726
00:34:21,260 --> 00:34:21,860
Mr. Cheng.

727
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:24,100
Mr. Cheng.

728
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:25,219
The commander has arrived.

729
00:34:25,219 --> 00:34:26,620
Officers and soldiers already lined up.

730
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:28,900
Mr. Shang.

731
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:30,699
Success or failure,

732
00:34:31,340 --> 00:34:33,179
you have to show your best.

733
00:34:33,739 --> 00:34:35,020
You will see.

734
00:34:41,020 --> 00:34:41,980
Cao.

735
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:43,300
Finally, you’re here.

736
00:34:43,699 --> 00:34:44,860
I’ve been waiting for you.

737
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:45,900
Waiting?

738
00:34:46,060 --> 00:34:48,300
I saw you running out from inside.

739
00:34:48,300 --> 00:34:49,820
Please forgive me.

740
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:51,260
It’s cold and windy

741
00:34:51,260 --> 00:34:51,980
outside.

742
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:52,980
I went in to avoid from wind.

743
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:54,699
You came as soon as I got in.

744
00:34:55,500 --> 00:34:58,380
The wind in Peking can melt you down?

745
00:35:00,140 --> 00:35:01,220
You are so week.

746
00:35:02,020 --> 00:35:03,260
Can you handle the business well

747
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:04,340
of your family?

748
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:05,860
I am lucky.

749
00:35:06,220 --> 00:35:08,580
I have you to help me with my business.

750
00:35:08,580 --> 00:35:09,980
I don’t have to do it myself.

751
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:12,900
You want to rely on me all the time?

752
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:14,100
Come.

753
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:15,660
Take the gifts in.

754
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:19,660
So many things.

755
00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:22,420
People may think they’re betrothal presents.

756
00:35:22,700 --> 00:35:24,660
I don’t have another sister to marry you.

757
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:26,060
There is

758
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:29,420
a train toy which can run on the ground.

759
00:35:29,860 --> 00:35:31,620
It can hoot.

760
00:35:32,540 --> 00:35:33,660
I’m sure you have never seen it.

761
00:35:34,820 --> 00:35:35,500
Is it so fun?

762
00:35:35,900 --> 00:35:37,740
I will play it before giving it to my son.

763
00:35:39,060 --> 00:35:39,700
You brat.

764
00:35:39,700 --> 00:35:40,220
Let’s go

765
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:41,020
and talk inside.

766
00:35:41,420 --> 00:35:42,620
Tell them the Commander comes.

767
00:35:42,620 --> 00:35:43,700
Start the banquet.

768
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:44,580
OK.

769
00:35:45,180 --> 00:35:45,820
No hurry.

770
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:47,940
Let’s have a talk first.

771
00:35:48,220 --> 00:35:48,860
Slowly.

772
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:52,060
Greetings.

773
00:35:56,820 --> 00:35:57,940
Ma’am.

774
00:35:57,940 --> 00:35:58,700
Greetings.

775
00:35:58,700 --> 00:35:59,940
What are you doing?

776
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:00,860
Put it down.

777
00:36:01,060 --> 00:36:02,260
What are you doing here?

778
00:36:02,260 --> 00:36:02,860
It’s fine.

779
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:03,940
I come to help.

780
00:36:04,460 --> 00:36:04,900
You...

781
00:36:04,900 --> 00:36:06,380
It’s your big day.

782
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:08,020
You don’t have enough men.

783
00:36:08,020 --> 00:36:09,180
So, we come to give you a hand.

784
00:36:09,180 --> 00:36:10,260
You shouldn’t.

785
00:36:10,260 --> 00:36:11,140
You’re guests.

786
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:13,420
We are not.

787
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:15,060
We're families.

788
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:17,780
You and your wife are kind to us.

789
00:36:17,780 --> 00:36:19,580
We mean to repay you.

790
00:36:19,580 --> 00:36:20,060
No.

791
00:36:20,060 --> 00:36:21,140
Don’t.

792
00:36:21,140 --> 00:36:22,220
If my sister knows this,

793
00:36:22,220 --> 00:36:23,620
she will scold me.

794
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:26,260
Go and get changed now.

795
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:27,780
Go to have food and wine at the hall.

796
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:30,780
What are you waiting for?

797
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:31,780
Cousin.

798
00:36:31,780 --> 00:36:33,060
Commander Cao is here.

799
00:36:33,580 --> 00:36:34,780
You work in the government.

800
00:36:34,780 --> 00:36:36,220
Go to meet him

801
00:36:36,220 --> 00:36:37,100
now.

802
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,100
It’s helpful

803
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,100
for your career.

804
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:39,620
No.

805
00:36:39,980 --> 00:36:41,700
I don’t want to have connections with officials.

806
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:44,060
Go ahead.

807
00:36:44,620 --> 00:36:45,260
I’ll stay and help here.

808
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:45,980
Rest assured.

809
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:48,060
Go ahead for your cousin’s sake.

810
00:36:48,060 --> 00:36:48,740
Ma’am.

811
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:49,780
It’s OK.

812
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:53,380
Cheng family is wealthy.

813
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:53,980
Look,

814
00:36:53,980 --> 00:36:54,900
some many people are working.

815
00:36:54,900 --> 00:36:56,140
You are not needed.

816
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,500
I will be angry.

817
00:36:58,740 --> 00:36:59,980
Hurry up. Go.

818
00:37:00,260 --> 00:37:00,740
Hey.

819
00:37:00,740 --> 00:37:01,500
Go and get changed.

820
00:37:01,500 --> 00:37:02,700
Take it off.

821
00:37:03,540 --> 00:37:04,060
Alright.

822
00:37:04,220 --> 00:37:04,780
Go.

823
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:07,420
The hazelnuts are bought from the north by my men.

824
00:37:08,260 --> 00:37:08,940
They’re good for health.

825
00:37:09,380 --> 00:37:10,060
Try them.

826
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:12,260
Don’t eat them

827
00:37:12,260 --> 00:37:13,100
too much.

828
00:37:13,460 --> 00:37:14,420
You’ll fart a lot.

829
00:37:15,740 --> 00:37:17,180
I’ll keep them if you don't like.

830
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:19,500
I’m kind to you,

831
00:37:19,860 --> 00:37:21,620
while you are not kind to me.

832
00:37:25,620 --> 00:37:26,540
Oh, right.

833
00:37:27,220 --> 00:37:29,500
Why doesn’t Young Master come here?

834
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:31,380
Young Master?

835
00:37:31,780 --> 00:37:32,780
Don’t mention him.

836
00:37:36,540 --> 00:37:39,420
Cao Guixiu is a bastard.

837
00:37:41,020 --> 00:37:41,780
What’s wrong with you?

838
00:37:42,580 --> 00:37:43,220
Commander.

839
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:44,740
Don’t say that.

840
00:37:45,180 --> 00:37:46,020
He’s your son.

841
00:37:46,500 --> 00:37:48,740
You are scolding yourself.

842
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:51,660
You know him.

843
00:37:52,780 --> 00:37:54,420
I ask him

844
00:37:54,420 --> 00:37:57,140
to study abroad

845
00:37:57,900 --> 00:38:01,100
and hope he can help me someday

846
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:02,420
when he’s back.

847
00:38:02,780 --> 00:38:04,020
But after he

848
00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:06,660
comes back from abroad,

849
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:09,020
he always behaves against me.

850
00:38:12,460 --> 00:38:13,940
He even met some

851
00:38:14,660 --> 00:38:16,980
strange guys days ago.

852
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:20,020
Strange guys?

853
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,620
Who are they?

854
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:25,060
I have no idea.

855
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:28,020
But they look suspicious and dangerous.

856
00:38:29,420 --> 00:38:30,260
Maybe

857
00:38:30,780 --> 00:38:33,580
they deserve bullets.

858
00:38:34,460 --> 00:38:35,940
He is my only son.

859
00:38:35,940 --> 00:38:38,180
otherwise, I could have shot him.

860
00:38:43,060 --> 00:38:43,660
How about this?

861
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:45,580
Let my sister

862
00:38:47,140 --> 00:38:48,220
have another baby for you.

863
00:38:48,460 --> 00:38:49,420
See if it’s OK.

864
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:50,740
If it’s OK,

865
00:38:52,100 --> 00:38:53,340
you may shoot Cao Guixiu.

866
00:38:53,580 --> 00:38:54,900
I’ll slap you.

867
00:38:55,420 --> 00:38:57,500
Only you dare to talk to me like this.

868
00:38:57,500 --> 00:38:58,500
I tell you.

869
00:39:01,380 --> 00:39:02,100
Cao.

870
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:04,500
You are so kind to me,

871
00:39:05,540 --> 00:39:08,980
while you are mean to Young Master.

872
00:39:09,620 --> 00:39:11,700
What is

873
00:39:12,060 --> 00:39:14,060
the unsettled grudge between you and your son?

874
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:16,700
Why not

875
00:39:17,420 --> 00:39:18,460
have a talk with him?

876
00:39:19,420 --> 00:39:20,540
Damn it.

877
00:39:21,100 --> 00:39:22,620
I am furious when he's mentioned.

878
00:39:23,660 --> 00:39:24,540
Don’t mention him.

879
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:28,260
Feng’er.

880
00:39:28,740 --> 00:39:30,780
May I see your son?

881
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:31,220
Cao.

882
00:39:31,220 --> 00:39:33,020
Don’t call me Feng’er.

883
00:39:33,140 --> 00:39:34,540
It’s a girl’s name.

884
00:39:34,620 --> 00:39:35,740
People will make fun of me

885
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:37,260
if they hear it.

886
00:39:39,780 --> 00:39:40,540
Feng’er.

887
00:39:41,540 --> 00:39:42,100
Feng’er.

888
00:39:43,220 --> 00:39:43,900
Feng’er.

889
00:39:46,500 --> 00:39:47,900
As you please.

890
00:39:50,020 --> 00:39:52,260
He is just a baby. Don’t see him.

891
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:53,700
Cao.

892
00:39:55,460 --> 00:39:55,940
Would you like

893
00:39:55,940 --> 00:39:57,980
to see something interesting?

894
00:39:58,500 --> 00:39:59,420
What is it?

895
00:40:00,340 --> 00:40:01,700
Let’s make a deal first.

896
00:40:02,580 --> 00:40:05,460
I don’t mean to anger you.

897
00:40:06,500 --> 00:40:08,020
Don’t get mad.

898
00:40:08,260 --> 00:40:09,500
I won’t let him come

899
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:11,260
if you will get mad.

900
00:40:12,500 --> 00:40:13,100
Him?

901
00:40:13,580 --> 00:40:14,260
Who?

902
00:40:20,580 --> 00:40:22,060
I ask Shang Xirui

903
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:24,420
to perform operas for us.

904
00:40:25,860 --> 00:40:27,540
Shang Xirui?

905
00:40:30,700 --> 00:40:33,500
That boy from Pingyang?

906
00:40:34,100 --> 00:40:35,180
Now

907
00:40:35,180 --> 00:40:38,980
Shang Xirui is rumored to be your foe.

908
00:40:39,500 --> 00:40:41,900
Theaters in Peking don’t allow him to perform.

909
00:40:42,260 --> 00:40:45,020
He is excluded and can’t even survive.

910
00:40:50,340 --> 00:40:52,260
He is just an actor.

911
00:40:52,900 --> 00:40:55,300
He doesn’t deserve to be my foe.

912
00:40:56,060 --> 00:40:57,940
As I expected.

913
00:40:58,460 --> 00:41:00,260
But I don’t know if it’s true.

914
00:41:01,380 --> 00:41:02,140
Cao.

915
00:41:02,460 --> 00:41:03,380
If it's true,

916
00:41:03,700 --> 00:41:05,540
I will let him leave right away.

917
00:41:06,780 --> 00:41:07,940
If it’s a rumor,

918
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:11,940
I’ll let him perform operas

919
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:14,260
and kowtow to you to apologize.

920
00:41:15,980 --> 00:41:17,020
Forget it.

921
00:41:17,540 --> 00:41:18,860
I know

922
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:21,540
that boy.

923
00:41:22,260 --> 00:41:24,220
He is tough.

924
00:41:24,900 --> 00:41:27,780
No need to let him kowtow and apologize.

925
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:30,220
If he will argue with me,

926
00:41:30,220 --> 00:41:32,140
I may shoot him.

927
00:41:32,460 --> 00:41:33,740
That’s ominous.

928
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:36,980
Listen.

929
00:41:37,860 --> 00:41:39,060
I haven’t watched operas

930
00:41:39,220 --> 00:41:40,220
for a long time.

931
00:41:40,940 --> 00:41:41,980
No other operas.

932
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:44,620
Qinqiang Opera first.

933
00:41:45,180 --> 00:41:46,380
As your wish.

934
00:41:49,260 --> 00:41:50,220
Mr. Cheng.

935
00:41:50,220 --> 00:41:51,500
Tell Mr. Shang

936
00:41:51,500 --> 00:41:52,780
to eat some food

937
00:41:53,140 --> 00:41:54,460
and get ready to perform

938
00:41:55,900 --> 00:41:57,420
Qinqiang Opera.

939
00:41:57,780 --> 00:41:59,780
Perform Qinqiang Opera now?

940
00:42:01,260 --> 00:42:02,740
I don’t prepare the outfits.

941
00:42:04,620 --> 00:42:06,780
How can I perform with the wrong outfits?

942
00:42:07,180 --> 00:42:08,740
That will be a joke.

943
00:42:09,780 --> 00:42:11,060
It’s unexpected.

944
00:42:11,260 --> 00:42:13,580
Command Cao ordered the opera himself.

945
00:42:13,660 --> 00:42:15,620
Mr. Cheng can’t reject it.

946
00:42:15,780 --> 00:42:16,620
Mr. Shang.

947
00:42:16,620 --> 00:42:17,660
Please try to

948
00:42:17,660 --> 00:42:19,260
satisfy him.

949
00:42:19,460 --> 00:42:19,980
Mr. Han.

950
00:42:19,980 --> 00:42:20,780
Come here quickly.

951
00:42:20,940 --> 00:42:22,380
You need to make the decision.

952
00:42:22,380 --> 00:42:22,900
OK.

953
00:42:22,900 --> 00:42:23,660
Coming.

954
00:42:23,940 --> 00:42:24,540
Fine.

955
00:42:24,540 --> 00:42:25,380
Go ahead.

956
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:26,420
No big deal.

957
00:42:26,900 --> 00:42:28,060
Thank you.

958
00:42:29,020 --> 00:42:29,780
Please

959
00:42:29,780 --> 00:42:31,940
enjoy the dishes.

960
00:42:32,180 --> 00:42:33,260
Excuse me.

961
00:42:39,660 --> 00:42:41,660
After all, he is a commander.

962
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:43,020
He gets what he wants right away.

963
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:44,220
An unavailable opera is ordered.

964
00:42:44,780 --> 00:42:45,580
Ridiculous.

965
00:42:46,660 --> 00:42:47,740
Can I have a drumstick?

966
00:42:48,060 --> 00:42:48,780
Yes, you can.

967
00:42:51,540 --> 00:42:52,580
What to do then?

968
00:42:53,060 --> 00:42:53,980
Perform without outfits?

969
00:42:56,660 --> 00:42:58,060
That’s a way out.

970
00:43:01,580 --> 00:43:03,140
The... The dishes aren’t good.

971
00:43:03,260 --> 00:43:04,260
Get some good food to me.

972
00:43:04,700 --> 00:43:05,140
OK.

973
00:43:05,140 --> 00:43:05,900
Sure.

974
00:43:06,260 --> 00:43:07,460
May I have all of it?

975
00:43:08,740 --> 00:43:09,500
Eat up.

976
00:43:11,740 --> 00:43:12,460
Remember it?

977
00:43:12,620 --> 00:43:13,940
It wasn’t brought here.

978
00:43:13,940 --> 00:43:14,780
Mrs. Cao.

979
00:43:15,500 --> 00:43:16,420
Mrs. Cao.

980
00:43:17,780 --> 00:43:18,540
What’s wrong?

981
00:43:19,180 --> 00:43:20,060
Mrs. Cao.

982
00:43:20,060 --> 00:43:21,380
Commander Cao has arrived.

983
00:43:21,380 --> 00:43:23,180
He is talking with Mr. Cheng.

984
00:43:23,180 --> 00:43:23,660
OK.

985
00:43:23,660 --> 00:43:24,660
I’m going to the kitchen first.

986
00:43:24,660 --> 00:43:25,700
Tell him I will go soon.

987
00:43:26,020 --> 00:43:26,460
OK.

988
00:43:29,660 --> 00:43:30,740
Who is that girl?

989
00:43:31,500 --> 00:43:32,860
Look familiar.

990
00:43:35,780 --> 00:43:36,940
Who is in that room?

991
00:43:38,140 --> 00:43:39,820
Troupe invited by Mr. Cheng.

992
00:43:41,620 --> 00:43:42,940
Which troupe?

993
00:43:42,940 --> 00:43:43,980
Shuiyun Theater.

994
00:43:46,660 --> 00:43:47,580
Let me ask you.

995
00:43:48,180 --> 00:43:49,900
Are Mrs. Cheng’s cousin and his wife invited?

996
00:43:49,900 --> 00:43:50,900
Yes.

997
00:43:54,140 --> 00:43:55,060
Crap.

998
00:43:55,420 --> 00:43:56,140
Well...
